flowchart LR
    A[User Interaction] --> B[Dispatch Action]
    B --> C{Async operation?}
    C -- Yes --> D[Middleware handles async]
    D --> E[API or IO call]
    E --> F[Dispatch Result Action]
    F --> G[Reducer or Mutation]
    C -- No --> G
    G --> H[Compute Next State]
    H --> I[Store Updated]
    I --> J[Notify Subscribed Components]
    J --> K{State slice changed?}
    K -- No --> L[Skip Re-render]
    K -- Yes --> M[Component Re-renders]
    M --> N[User Sees Updated UI]
    style N fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
